'''''The Empire Strikes Back Monthly'' 153''' is the one hundred fifty-third issue of the ''[[The Empire Strikes Back Monthly]]'' series of comic reprints, published in [[January]] [[1982]].

This issue features one of the few original comic stories in the series, "[[Dark Knight's Devilry]]". It was later reprinted and colorized in [[Classic Star Wars: Devilworlds 1|''Classic Star Wars: Devilworlds'' 1]].

==Contents==
*"[[Dark Knight's Devilry]]"
*"Tales of the Watcher"
*"Killraven: Warrior of Mars"

